PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778234501
OL,3,CAndy Burnham drops out of keynote
OL,4,Cspeech morning after local elections
OL,6,FBut on Thursday evening, organisers
OL,7,Fsaid he was being replaced by Caroline
OL,8,FSimpson, group chief executive of the
OL,9,FGreater Manchester Combined Authority,
OL,10,Fin the line-up. A spokesperson for the
OL,11,Fchildren's commissioner's office
OL,12,Fconfirmed to the Press Association
OL,13,Fthat Mr Burnham will not be attending
OL,14,Fthe event at all.
OL,16,FReports have suggested Mr Burnham has
OL,17,Fa plan to return to Westminster within
OL,18,Fweeks and wants to challenge the Prime
OL,19,FMinister.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
