OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778234501
OL,3,CAndy Burnham drops out of keynote
OL,4,Cspeech morning after local elections
OL,6,FVoters went to the polls on Thursday
OL,7,Ffor the Scottish and Welsh
OL,8,Fparliaments, as well as for local
OL,9,Fcouncils across England in the biggest
OL,10,Ftest of public opinion since the
OL,11,Fgeneral election in 2024.
OL,13,FThere have been reports that MPs are
OL,14,Fmoving to oust the Prime Minister in
OL,15,Fthe wake of the elections, in a
OL,16,Fbloodless coup modelled on the way Sir
OL,17,FTony Blair was encouraged to make way
OL,18,Ffor his successor Gordon Brown.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
