FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778234501
OL,3,CAndy Burnham drops out of keynote
OL,4,Cspeech morning after local elections
OL,6,FReports of backbench plans to move
OL,7,Fagainst Sir Keir come amid rumblings
OL,8,Fof a potential leadership tilt by
OL,9,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting, former
OL,10,Fdeputy prime minister Angela Rayner or
OL,11,FMr Burnham.
OL,13,FAllies of Ms Rayner are confident she
OL,14,Fwould be able to gain the support of
OL,15,Fthe 81 MPs required to launch a
OL,16,Fchallenge, a number which Mr Streeting
OL,17,Fis also said to have met, though
OL,18,Fneither are said to want to be the
OL,19,Ffirst to move.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778234501
OL,3,CAndy Burnham drops out of keynote
OL,4,Cspeech morning after local elections
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Mr Burnham has been tipped
OL,7,Fas a party favourite to succeed the
OL,8,FPrime Minister but he would have
OL,9,Fseveral logistical obstacles to clear
OL,10,Fbefore returning to Westminster should
OL,11,Fhe seek to mount a bid for No 10.
OL,13,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor has
OL,14,Fidentified several seats where MPs are
OL,15,Fprepared to step aside, triggering a
OL,16,Fby-election which could pave the way
OL,17,Ffor his return to Parliament,
OL,18,Faccording to The Guardian.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778234501
OL,3,CAndy Burnham drops out of keynote
OL,4,Cspeech morning after local elections
OL,6,FThe newspaper also reported Mr
OL,7,FBurnham's supporters are attempting to
OL,8,Favoid a formal leadership challenge
OL,9,Fagainst the Prime Minister, and hope
OL,10,Fto kickstart a process for him to
OL,11,Fstand down after Labour's results in
OL,12,Fthe local elections.
OL,14,FMr Burnham was earlier this year
OL,15,Fblocked by Labour's ruling National
OL,16,FExecutive Committee (NEC) from
OL,17,Fstanding in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,18,Felection after the previous MP Andrew
OL,19,FGwynne stood down, citing health
OL,20,Freasons.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778234501
OL,3,CAndy Burnham drops out of keynote
OL,4,Cspeech morning after local elections
OL,6,FThe NEC, which included Sir Keir, said
OL,7,Fworries about the costs of running a
OL,8,Fnew Manchester mayoral election and
OL,9,Ffear that Reform could take the
OL,10,Fmayoralty were behind the decision to
OL,11,Fblock Mr Burnham.
OL,13,FMr Burnham, who served as health
OL,14,Fsecretary in Gordon Brown's
OL,15,Fgovernment, is also said to be
OL,16,Fpreparing a progressive policy
OL,17,Fplatform for government, according to
OL,18,Fthe Guardian.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
